OL,6,FThe woman complained that her mother
OL,7,Fhad experienced poor general care at
OL,8,Fthe home including inadequate
OL,9,Fnutrition and dietary care. She
OL,10,Fexplained how her mother had lost a
OL,11,Fsignificant amount of weight while she
OL,12,Fwas a resident there and had ten falls
OL,13,Fduring her stay.
