OL,7,Frespect to cleaning issues, food
OL,8,Fprovision and data breaches in
OL,9,Frelation to the complaint. The Chief
OL,10,FExecutive of the organisation
OL,11,Fapologised to the daughter and
OL,12,Fdetailed actions that he had
OL,13,Fimplemented to ensure that similar
OL,14,Ffaults do not happen again.
